== Traditional, indigenous, and folk religions == {{Main articles|Folk religion}}{{See also|Paganism|Animism|Totemism|Shamanism|Mysticism}} Religions that consist of the traditional customs and beliefs of particular ethnic groups, refined and expanded upon for thousands of years, often lacking formal doctrine.
